Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前  被稱作血腥約翰的連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺害了我的妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后我們一直在追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稱之為"布萊克組織"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織里還有些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  法官  聯調局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一個有秘密需要掩蓋的執法人員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個腐敗警察的秘密組織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰是成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我說了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告訴我殺她的人  也就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底誰是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們很高興地宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終于確認了他的身份與面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執法部門負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖局長  就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手里有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦法官的令狀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局現在要關閉你們部門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了  這里沒我們的事兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會放棄  我不信你會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的情況我們已經無法掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持聯絡  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切  我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興你能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上塞車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一有空就過來見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況真是一團糟  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聽著  我覺得我們...  -一會兒有你說的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們現在肯定都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道接下來會發生什么事  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-探員  -所以我來說明下接下來會發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會找你們每個人談話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單獨談話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有權委托律師或工會代表隨行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你們自己選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為何需要律師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們考慮得長遠點  金寶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的上司伯特侖是個罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有可能你們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會非常仔細地審視你們每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們有任何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一點點可疑的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都會發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后起訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  除非
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們能夠配合  那我們會非常非常滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣你們就有點回旋的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(194.4,267.2)}加州  薩克拉門托  富蘭克林區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局展開一場全球輯兇行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通緝著名的薩克拉門托執法部門官員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局方面證實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據信伯特侖就是臭名昭著的連環殺手血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他因在整個加利福尼亞州中心地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯下一系列恐怖兇案而被通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這有公用電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里  你好啊  給我張六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一根菠蘿味雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六合彩  雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用不著捏著嗓子講話  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺真奇怪啊  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們上次...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伯特侖  還在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你問的是簡  那我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去樓上找過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也許還沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約一小時前  蓋爾·伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在薩城東區的一個加油站殺了一個警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你聽說了伯特侖當時在加油站做什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在打公用電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜他打給了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是簡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為你清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒法左右你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為你的男朋友和一名危險的逃犯勾結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為他已經深陷布萊克組織中無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是  他也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡無法阻止打給他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他也不是我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太遺憾了  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個好警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在依舊是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你們在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們聽說了伯特侖今早干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說聯調局的人在找我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在是怎樣  你們就躲在停車場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是躲起來  只是潛伏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們暫時還安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少現在還沒有下達對我們的逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們遲早會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她剛已經問了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今加調局已經不復存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能靠自己了  你們得保護好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不知道簡在哪里  他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想知道  明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-明白  頭兒  -明白  頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已經不是你們的頭兒了  關鍵就在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(191.4,278.4)}加州  薩克拉門托  威廉蘭德公園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被通緝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說真的  艾伯特給你下了逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你到底要不要告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦對  伯特侖打給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他想說什么  他那時沒時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么他還在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他會很快再打來告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手機不安全  聯調局...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  他們裝了竊聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們還沒追蹤到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們追蹤到了  我現在就早該被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許如此  但他們早晚會追蹤到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在伯特侖打來之前我不能扔掉手機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以事情就懸在這了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在閃爍其詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鳥的眼睛圓又亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《小恐龍》[系列童書]  你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很清楚他的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  -很抱歉我那時不得不掛電話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天實在太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系  這個電話不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你一百美元換你的手機  行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩百美元換你的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什么騙局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百美元  外加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部替代機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥們  我一會兒再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交易愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了  伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛才到底說了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我們應該見面好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就我們倆  -就像約會一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  游戲結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得說你我確實不分伯仲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在一切都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的覺得我們應該好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停戰  不帶武器  不玩花招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就談談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后各行其道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,談談  談什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我們都需要結束此事了  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在今天  現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我時間有點緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道能否相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到現在了就別膽小了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有那么多機會殺你  卻都沒下手  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  時間  地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小時后弗里蒙特公園的噴泉邊見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不知道那個地方  中央汽車站見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-北入口  -不行  那里人太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且警察太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道亞歷山大公墓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西門那邊有個小教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊  半小時之后見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別遲到  我不能待太久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小時之后見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想見我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去見他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我知道自己在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別去  你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局馬上就要抓到伯特侖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想他落在聯調局手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這一天早晚會來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不想讓你牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牽扯  我早就深陷其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要借你的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  你的槍  我不會開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是壯壯膽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎  相信我  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,疑犯逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責人呢  艾伯特在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手舉到我能看見的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特在哪兒  我必須得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  淡定點  伙計們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又不是阿爾·卡彭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}著名黑幫老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出來你是個正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以我的名義發誓  我一小時之內就回去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在  我...  我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別別別  告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么  你需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去見誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回局里說怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  讓她過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  里斯本女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是咱們兩個警察間幫個忙  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  我發誓到時候一定把他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們到底有什么緊急的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是跟伯特侖有約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-加調局  你給我退后  -怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  艾伯特  他什么也沒做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興見到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來不想提的  但加調局已經不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的警徽就是個玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你們只是在假扮警察
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你怎么說  放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是纏上我了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纏上聯調局了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你是真的聯調局探員  有什么證據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你們也許是布萊克組織的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出證明來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手下里德·史密斯就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么不可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們怎么知道簡會不會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾伯特探員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在確保他的安全之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護好他是我們的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  放下槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都放下槍  沒必要起沖突
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開我的車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓他走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了  就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你們的槍都放到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照他說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追蹤里斯本探員的車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在我車上裝了追蹤器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我們怎么能找到簡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過認識你們這些人我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我知道你們早晚要出簍子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能省我不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不應驗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還沒準備好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我看會兒車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  會看好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  伙計  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思麻煩你了  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我長話短說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿不愿意載我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里是四隊  我們看見那輛車了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停在第五大道和謝爾曼街交會處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后  先退后  他們可能就在那兒接頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四隊  什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四隊  回答  該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  里斯本車里就幾個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有發現簡  重復  我們沒發現簡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否收...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再越錯越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是不見棺材不落淚是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  我們真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  你居然還叫他長官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別激動  "頭號公敵"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}約翰.格林杰是蕭條時期聯調局追捕的最著名的黑幫頭目  曾兩度越獄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在是階下囚  還是識相點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  你是想住好一點的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝[西語]  奧雷利奧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣  祝你好運[西語]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:07.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(78,97.6)}安琪拉·蘿斯金·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:07.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(316.2,99)}夏洛特·安妮·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先得搜搜你身上有沒有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你才能進去  把手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.35,0:23:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試下也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你這么準時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還真是倆無賴  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.87,0:24:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證  這是最后一次騙你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先說正事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和聯調局犯了個嚴重的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.16,0:24:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉讓你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我只是布萊克組織
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.20,0:24:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一員卑微走卒罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰可是高層
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.17,0:25:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是很相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信隨你  但
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.60,0:25:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們草率得出的結論是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.98,0:25:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么誰是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.85,0:25:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.92,0:25:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.85,0:25:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.99,0:25:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織嚴格遵循的原則是只須知道必需的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.26,0:25:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.73,0:25:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我們完全可以在電話里說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.15,0:25:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我們在電話里說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.81,0:25:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你  你可能就不會來見我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.41,0:25:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.53,0:25:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到命令要打電話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.47,0:25:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你游戲結束  安排和你見面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.58,0:25:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.54,0:25:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么要我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.23,0:25:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你不要以為
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.65,0:25:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我樂意這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.58,0:25:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織不想有遺留問題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.96,0:25:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想留下把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.87,0:25:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.36,0:26:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手吧  奧斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.15,0:26:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別  別  聽著  聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.33,0:26:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們談談  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.79,0:26:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  這不是我能決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.01,0:26:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很喜歡你  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.59,0:26:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別  別  不需要這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.89,0:26:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.39,0:26:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  奧斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.70,0:26:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以出去等著了  就...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.34,0:26:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確保沒人來打擾我們
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.72,0:26:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.68,0:27:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.16,0:27:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯  你在干
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.71,0:27:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.38,0:27:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不如周呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.14,0:27:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們必須告訴我們到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.77,0:27:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不需要做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.75,0:27:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也什么都做不了  行行好就放松點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.09,0:27:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  我怎么放松得下來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.14,0:27:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有時候表現的好像你很享受無助感
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.89,0:27:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我收回  別放松
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.77,0:27:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用額頭把車窗撞破
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.97,0:27:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就可以跳車跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.05,0:27:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙計們  團結一點好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.00,0:27:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.57,0:27:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"抱歉"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.60,0:27:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫林斯  你是本地人  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.04,0:27:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  林肯高地的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.31,0:27:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-給我弄一張薩克拉門托的地圖  -是  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.07,0:27:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車里的電腦上就有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.90,0:27:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紙質地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.30,0:27:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紙質  地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:27:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點去找
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.57,0:28:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有紙質地圖嗎
